snippet: The suspect in the shooting rampage that left six people dead and three wounded at a Sikh temple in Wisconsin on Sunday has been identified as Wade M. Page, law enforcement officials announced on Monday.
abstract: The suspect in the shooting rampage that left six people dead and three wounded at a Sikh temple in Wisconsin on Sunday has been identified as Wade M. Page, law enforcement officials announced on Monday.

headline.main: Wisconsin Gunman Identified as U.S. Army Veteran
